OL,3,CNew test to prevent newborn babies
OL,4,Cgoing deaf to be trialled across the UK
OL,6,FThe test replaces a previous method
OL,7,Fthat took several days and is the
OL,8,Ffirst use of a rapid point of care
OL,9,Fgenetic test in acute neonatal care.
OL,11,FIt is thought that the bedside test
OL,12,Fcould save the NHS #5 million every
OL,13,Fyear by reducing the need for
OL,14,Finterventions, such as cochlear
OL,15,Fimplants.
OL,17,FA two-year study will trial the test
OL,18,Fat large intensive care units as well
OL,19,Fas small special care baby units.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
