OL,3,CNew test to prevent newborn babies
OL,4,Cgoing deaf to be trialled across the UK
OL,6,FThe genetic test was first piloted at
OL,7,FSaint Mary's Hospital and Liverpool
OL,8,FWomen's Hospital in 2020 as part of
OL,9,Fthe an earlier study.
OL,11,FIt was then implemented into routine
OL,12,Fclinical practice at various Greater
OL,13,FManchester maternity units in 2022 and
OL,14,F2023.
OL,16,FThe National Institute for Health and
OL,17,FCare Excellence (NICE) conditionally
OL,18,Frecommended the Genedrive test for use
OL,19,Fin the NHS last year.
