OL,3,CNew test to prevent newborn babies
OL,4,Cgoing deaf to be trialled across the UK
OL,6,FIt is now in use at eight Greater
OL,7,FManchester neonatal units and has has
OL,8,Fprevented the hearing loss of 11
OL,9,Fbabies across the region, with 4,000
OL,10,Fbabies tested as of October 2024.
OL,12,FThe study, named PALOH-UK, is going to
OL,13,Fbe funded by #1.4 million from the
OL,14,FNational Institute for Health and Care
OL,15,FResearch (NIHR) and the Office for
OL,16,FLife Sciences.
