OL,3,CNew test to prevent newborn babies
OL,4,Cgoing deaf to be trialled across the UK
OL,6,FDr John McDermott, Clinical Geneticist
OL,7,Fat MFT and joint lead for the PALOH-UK
OL,8,Fstudy said: "We are incredibly proud
OL,9,Fto be leading this research at MFT,
OL,10,Fhaving already seen the difference
OL,11,Fthis new genetic test has made across
OL,12,FGreater Manchester.
OL,14,F"We are excited to explore how it can
OL,15,Fbe used effectively at other neonatal
OL,16,Funits across the UK.
