OL,3,CNew test to prevent newborn babies
OL,4,Cgoing deaf to be trialled across the UK
OL,6,F"The PALOH-UK study will demonstrate
OL,7,Fhow the test can be used in a timely
OL,8,Fway to ensure babies get a safe,
OL,9,Feffective antibiotic without affecting
OL,10,Fnormal clinical practice, on a much
OL,11,Flarger scale."
OL,13,FThe study will begin in November 2024.
